data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_08615c0c6fc463110069af439b6ae881959ca7d00ae85b757d","logprobs":[],"output_index":0,"sequence_number":172,"text":"Given the sunny weather and comfortable temperature in Toronto, here are some activities you might consider:\n\n1. **Visit a Park**: Enjoy a stroll or a picnic in one of Toronto's beautiful parks, like High Park or Trinity Bellwoods.\n\n2. **Outdoor Café**: Relax at an outdoor café and enjoy a coffee or lunch while soaking up the sun.\n\n3. **Bike Ride**: Rent a bike and explore the waterfront or the many bike paths around the city.\n\n4. **Visit the Toronto Islands**: Take a ferry to the Toronto Islands for a day of exploration, beach time, or just enjoying the views of the city skyline.\n\n5. **Outdoor Markets**: Check out a local farmers' market or street fair for fresh produce and local crafts.\n\nThese activities will allow you to make the most of the pleasant weather!"}

